Mediaset May Get Italy Approval on DMT Purchase, Radiocor Says

-- B y   C h i a r a   V a s a r r i   a n d   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 
2011-12-13T20:03:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-13/mediaset-may-get-italy-approval-on-dmt-purchase-radiocor-says.html
Italy’s competition watchdog may
give preliminary approval to  Mediaset SpA (MS) ’s purchase of  Digital
Multimedia Technologies SpA (DMT)  as soon as tomorrow on certain
conditions, news agency Radiocor reported, citing a document
issued by the regulator.  Mediaset will be required to grant all television operators
non-discriminatory access to infrastructure and to publish a
price list, Radiocor reported citing the document.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Chiara Vasarri in Rome at 
 cvasarri@bloomberg.net ;
Chiara Remondini in Milan at 
 cremondini@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story: Angela Cullen
at   acullen8@bloomberg.net  